01:14:04,480 --> 01:14:11,600
I can change the world right here in this upside-down airfield.

1572
01:14:13,039 --> 01:14:15,039
This is amazing.

1573
01:14:17,280 --> 01:14:17,840
All right.

1574
01:14:17,840 --> 01:14:20,320
I'm going to go ahead and get ready.

1575
01:14:20,319 --> 01:14:26,719
So, you guys see Dents go off into the corner, which you didn't notice before.

1576
01:14:27,599 --> 01:14:34,399
Somehow he pulled out like a hood, and he's got this hood on his head, and he's just

1577
01:14:34,399 --> 01:14:35,759
like kind of bouncing around.

1578
01:14:37,279 --> 01:14:39,599
He's saying things like spaghetti, spaghetti.

1579
01:14:39,599 --> 01:14:41,599
It's just...

1580
01:14:43,119 --> 01:14:43,599
Yeah.

1581
01:14:43,920 --> 01:14:48,960
So, he's just...

1582
01:14:48,960 --> 01:14:49,680
He's really...

1583
01:14:50,400 --> 01:14:54,880
You know that he's been serious before, but he hasn't been serious.

1584
01:14:54,880 --> 01:14:58,240
But now, Dents is serious.

1585
01:14:59,520 --> 01:15:00,480
He's ready to go.

1586
01:15:01,039 --> 01:15:01,600
You ready?

1587
01:15:01,600 --> 01:15:02,480
It's time to get on.

1588
01:15:03,920 --> 01:15:04,420
Okay.

1589
01:15:05,760 --> 01:15:06,560
Hey, everybody.

1590
01:15:06,560 --> 01:15:08,160
Me, Shiny Turd, here again.

1591
01:15:08,960 --> 01:15:11,840
Getting you ready before Puffy comes on.

1592
01:15:12,000 --> 01:15:15,279
We got a new kid in town.

1593
01:15:15,279 --> 01:15:16,239
Open it up for Puffy.

1594
01:15:16,239 --> 01:15:17,520
Give him a warm welcome.

1595
01:15:17,520 --> 01:15:18,319
It's Dents.

1596
01:15:18,319 --> 01:15:22,480
We're like clapping, freaking out.

1597
01:15:23,920 --> 01:15:31,119
Dents comes in, and he flaps his wings, and he sits there, and he looks around,

1598
01:15:31,119 --> 01:15:34,239
and he goes, oh, wait a minute.

1599
01:15:36,000 --> 01:15:40,239
Are you guys ready to laugh?

1600
01:15:42,319 --> 01:15:44,079
Don't laugh too hard.

1601
01:15:44,079 --> 01:15:46,000
I don't want to get singed.

1602
01:15:50,800 --> 01:15:55,039
It's uproarious laughter, because dragon puns go over very well.

1603
01:15:57,760 --> 01:15:58,260
So...

1604
01:16:00,000 --> 01:16:04,480
So, you guys live in an upside-down anthill.

1605
01:16:05,760 --> 01:16:11,360
But what happens when you fart?

1606
01:16:12,400 --> 01:16:17,840
If someone farts and someone else laughs, does the whole room go up in flames?

1607
01:16:21,760 --> 01:16:23,199
I was just curious.

1608
01:16:28,960 --> 01:16:31,279
We fade out on Dents' performance.

1609
01:16:31,279 --> 01:16:34,800
Laughter uproarious throughout, and we check back in.

1610
01:16:35,840 --> 01:16:37,920
As Dents, you join back with your group.

1611
01:16:38,079 --> 01:16:40,720
That was great, I think.

1612
01:16:40,720 --> 01:16:42,319
What did you guys think?

1613
01:16:43,199 --> 01:16:44,560
Oh, that was...

1614
01:16:45,440 --> 01:16:46,800
I'm crying still.

1615
01:16:46,800 --> 01:16:48,159
It was so funny.

1616
01:16:48,159 --> 01:16:49,279
Oh, my god.

1617
01:16:49,279 --> 01:16:52,159
We hadn't had the chance to see you perform before.

1618
01:16:52,159 --> 01:16:52,880
You killed it up there.

1619
01:16:52,880 --> 01:16:53,840
Oh, it was really amazing.

1620
01:16:53,840 --> 01:16:55,359
Wow, wow.

1621
01:16:55,359 --> 01:16:57,440
Oh, well, thank you.

1622
01:16:57,440 --> 01:17:00,960
I think you really found Janeshia with these dragon puns.

1623
01:17:00,960 --> 01:17:02,880
I don't know, maybe.

1624
01:17:02,880 --> 01:17:03,760
Let me...

1625
01:17:03,760 --> 01:17:06,079
Oh, I'm going to go find Janeshia.

1626
01:17:06,559 --> 01:17:11,920
Oh, I'm going to go find Shiny Turd, because maybe he'll give me some money.

1627
01:17:12,720 --> 01:17:13,519
I bet he will.

1628
01:17:13,519 --> 01:17:14,399
He's going to want you.

1629
01:17:14,399 --> 01:17:15,359
He definitely will.

1630
01:17:15,359 --> 01:17:17,039
Oh, you are such a hit.

1631
01:17:17,039 --> 01:17:18,960
I think you're going to be a huge star.

1632
01:17:18,960 --> 01:17:21,039
The three of you see it before Dents does,

1633
01:17:21,039 --> 01:17:24,640
but Dents, you turn around and standing behind you is puff.

1634
01:17:28,000 --> 01:17:28,500
Hey!

1635
01:17:30,319 --> 01:17:33,600
No one has ever killed that good before me, ever!

1636
01:17:34,240 --> 01:17:35,440
Oh, well.

1637
01:17:36,240 --> 01:17:37,920
I want you to come on the road with me.

1638
01:17:37,920 --> 01:17:39,440
What do you think there, Dents?

1639
01:17:40,960 --> 01:17:41,680
Wait, is...

1640
01:17:44,320 --> 01:17:47,760
Are we going to perform not on the road?

1641
01:17:50,640 --> 01:17:54,880
Yeah, we're going to perform in the clubs

1642
01:17:55,600 --> 01:17:58,560
and then go on the road to get to the clubs.

1643
01:17:59,840 --> 01:18:00,880
Oh, wait a minute.

1644
01:18:02,000 --> 01:18:03,440
And we'll get paid too.

1645
01:18:03,600 --> 01:18:04,800
Sign this piece of paper.

1646
01:18:04,800 --> 01:18:06,079
Oh, I've got a lot of papers to sign.

1647
01:18:06,079 --> 01:18:09,360
Mia called ahead, said you got to get the paperwork first.

1648
01:18:09,360 --> 01:18:10,400
Oh, yes.

1649
01:18:10,400 --> 01:18:11,680
Yeah, I've got some paperwork.

1650
01:18:12,240 --> 01:18:15,600
So wait a minute, I can sign this paperwork and that paperwork

1651
01:18:15,600 --> 01:18:16,560
and then I'll get...

1652
01:18:16,560 --> 01:18:17,680
I'll have two jobs.

1653
01:18:18,720 --> 01:18:19,220
Yep.

1654
01:18:19,920 --> 01:18:20,400
Oh, I'm sorry.

1655
01:18:20,400 --> 01:18:21,760
Yep, if this one falls through.

1656
01:18:23,520 --> 01:18:25,680
Second guessing, quite a few things.

1657
01:18:27,200 --> 01:18:27,840
Oh, okay.

1658
01:18:29,680 --> 01:18:30,800
I probably should get

1659
01:18:31,199 --> 01:18:35,199
my manager to read through this and he hands it to Sully.

1660
01:18:37,199 --> 01:18:39,440
Sully takes it and takes a pair of glasses.

1661
01:18:39,440 --> 01:18:41,920
No one knows where he got them from out of his pocket.

1662
01:18:43,279 --> 01:18:46,320
Puts them on his face and just like peruses.

1663
01:18:47,360 --> 01:18:53,360
Licks his finger, flips it, makes a little like note

1664
01:18:53,360 --> 01:18:56,640
or like changes somewhere and like initials beside it.

1665
01:18:56,640 --> 01:18:58,480
It's like, yeah, no, it looks pretty good.

1666
01:18:58,560 --> 01:19:00,800
I made a couple of suggested changes there,

1667
01:19:00,800 --> 01:19:03,040
but I mean, all in all, it looks real solid.

1668
01:19:03,040 --> 01:19:05,120
I would definitely take this dance.

1669
01:19:05,120 --> 01:19:06,240
I would definitely take this.

1670
01:19:06,880 --> 01:19:10,320
Oh my gosh, this is amazing.

1671
01:19:10,320 --> 01:19:14,800
And he signs it and he hands the note back over to Puff.

1672
01:19:16,160 --> 01:19:22,560
We'll get started right away, but first I must do one thing.

1673
01:19:23,360 --> 01:19:26,240
And he turns back around and he kneels down

1674
01:19:27,199 --> 01:19:29,439
so that he's eye level with Sully.

1675
01:19:30,880 --> 01:19:37,199
And he says, Sully, you were my first friend

1676
01:19:38,000 --> 01:19:40,159
that I met three weeks ago.

1677
01:19:42,719 --> 01:19:51,439
And you became my manager, just like Glim prophesied.

1678
01:19:52,960 --> 01:19:54,559
You changed my life.

1679
01:19:56,319 --> 01:20:04,960
Allow me to change yours because sometimes you get in fights

1680
01:20:05,760 --> 01:20:07,119
and you need protection.

1681
01:20:08,000 --> 01:20:10,639
So please take this.

1682
01:20:10,639 --> 01:20:15,679
And he reaches back behind his back, unsheathes his sword

1683
01:20:15,679 --> 01:20:20,079
or pulls it out off of, unbuckles it from himself

1684
01:20:21,039 --> 01:20:25,760
and hands over sheath and all the frightful sword of reflection.

1685
01:20:26,559 --> 01:20:27,279
To Sully.

1686
01:20:28,079 --> 01:20:30,159
Sully grabs it and holds it in his arms.

1687
01:20:31,599 --> 01:20:32,880
You didn't have to do this.

1688
01:20:34,079 --> 01:20:35,519
I'm really touched.

1689
01:20:35,519 --> 01:20:39,599
I just, I don't, so like in emotions and stuff,

1690
01:20:39,599 --> 01:20:44,800
so like you take care of yourself and it's brilliant.

1691
01:20:44,800 --> 01:20:47,359
Guys, did you see he gave me a sword?

1692
01:20:47,359 --> 01:20:49,039
Yeah, that super cool shiny one.

1693
01:20:50,239 --> 01:20:52,159
I feel like I need a sword now.

1694
01:20:52,159 --> 01:20:53,439
Everyone else has swords.

1695
01:20:54,400 --> 01:20:56,080
I mean, there's everything in the marketplace.

1696
01:20:56,080 --> 01:20:57,840
We can swing by the robe place tomorrow.

1697
01:20:57,840 --> 01:20:59,280
We can probably get you a new sword.

1698
01:20:59,280 --> 01:20:59,760
I don't know.

1699
01:20:59,760 --> 01:21:00,960
I think they have everything here.

1700
01:21:02,160 --> 01:21:06,880
You take care of yourself, Dent and Sully chokes a little bit.

1701
01:21:07,920 --> 01:21:14,320
Well, let me just tell you, if you guys see us in town,

1702
01:21:17,520 --> 01:21:21,760
you will definitely have a seat right up in the front.

1703
01:21:22,239 --> 01:21:24,560
Wherever we go.

1704
01:21:24,560 --> 01:21:25,600
We wouldn't miss it.

1705
01:21:28,640 --> 01:21:29,600
That's awesome.

1706
01:21:33,600 --> 01:21:36,239
The crowd cheers as Puff takes the stage

1707
01:21:36,239 --> 01:21:40,239
