1730
01:23:39,280 --> 01:23:43,200
He's not there yet, but he's leaning in that direction, for sure.

1731
01:23:43,519 --> 01:23:45,279
I just need a bit of decoupage, man.

1732
01:23:45,279 --> 01:23:46,079
It's just fine.

1733
